==English==

===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ædəl|-ædəl]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

#An [[oar]] used for [[propelling]] a [[boat]] through [[water]]
#A two-handed, single-bladed [[oar]] used for [[canoe]]ing
#A double-bladed [[oar]] used for [[kayak]]ing
#A [[slat]] of a [[paddleboat]]'s [[wheel]]
# {{UK}} a [[meandering]] [[walk]] through [[shallow]] [[water]], especially at the [[seaside]]

